==English==
===Noun===
{{en-noun|s|-}}

# {{uncountable}} the act of [[tying]] something
# {{countable}} a [[cord]] etc used to [[tie]] something, especially the [[thread]] used in [[surgery]] to [[close]] a [[vessel]] or [[duct]]
# {{countable}} a [[character]], such as æ, that [[combine]]s [[multiple]] [[letter]]s
# {{countable}} {{music}} a group of [[note]]s played as a [[phrase]]; the [[curve]]d [[line]] that [[indicate]]s such a phrase
# {{countable}} a piece used to hold the [[reed]] to the [[mouthpiece]] on [[woodwind]] instruments

